long.am,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,en,en_AU,en_GB,en_US,e:
Take notes. Set Reminders. Publish blogs and websites.

Unique mind-map style design helps you organize.

If you're like me, you're pumping out notes like a mad wizard, and normal notepads won't cut it – you've got a detailed mind and too many notes – some short, some long – on multiple devices.

• Themes
• Truly rich notes
• Lists
• Reminders
• Highlight + Share
• Sync w/ your devices
• Day + Night Editor
• Blog + Website Publishing
• Free

Check out the MindSky Web Clipper extension to save and clear clutter from articles, highlight text, and share clutter-free highlighted articles with others.
